Mahajot is grand or broad alliance that some political parties proposed to form for fighting communist government in West Bengal in India. It was to be led by Trinamool Congress with Indian National Congress and Bharatiya Janata Party both included in the alliance.People regards this alliance as one of the "major mistakes of the history".


